      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been truly loved? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in solid shape, runs super smooth, and is totally ready for your next big road trip or just your daily commute! I've taken great care of it, and I'd love to see it go to a great home. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
