    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sorted E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies. This example benefits from documented subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS service, addressing the platform's primary longevity concerns. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise shift gates, transferring power through a healthy M-Variable differential. The chassis is stabilized by upgraded Bilstein B6 dampers and poly-bushings, maintaining the sharp turn-in the chassis is known for. A true driver\u2019s car with a solid powertrain and a clean title.",
      "price": 34800.0,
