    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a well-cared-for 2018 Audi S5 Sportback finished in striking Navarra Blue Metallic over a Magma Red leather interior. This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between executive luxury and spirited performance. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss luster, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with regular road use. The 19-inch 5-spoke Cavo wheels are in great shape with only a small scuff on the rear passenger rim. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of tech and comfort; the Nappa leather seats are supple, showing only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All electronics, including the Audi Virtual Cockpit and the panoramic sunroof, operate flawlessly. Under the hood, the 3.0L turbocharged V6 runs smooth and pulls strong. I have maintained a rigorous service schedule, with the most recent oil change and multi-point inspection completed just 1,000 miles ago. The tires have approximately 70% tread life remaining, and the brake pads were replaced last season. This is a clean, honest example of a modern classic that is ready for the open road.",
      "price": 34500.0,
